    q: "My patio heater is 12 years old. Repair or replace?",
    a: "Depends on the brand and what failed. AEI Sunpak and Bromic Platinum at 12 years with thermocouple or ignition failures are usually worth repairing. The burner and reflector are still good. Cheaper brands at 12 years with gas valve failures, usually replace. We tell you on-site after diagnosis.",
  },
  {
    q: "What's your warranty?",
    a: "90 days parts and labor on every repair. If we replace your thermocouple and it fails in 90 days, we replace it again at no charge. Same policy across the company.",
